# Database Tables

## Calls
- id
- caller_name
- callback_number
- pickup_location
- pickup_department
- pickup_room
- pickup_time
- appointment_duration
- dropoff_location
- dropoff_department
- dropoff_room
- notes
- assigned_unit_id
- status (Pending / Assigned / Completed)

## Patients
- id
- first_name
- last_name
- date_of_birth
- address
- condition
- call_id

## Insurance
- id
- patient_id
- insurance_type (Primary / Secondary / Tertiary)
- company_name
- policy_number
- authorization_number

## Units / Trucks
- id
- unit_number
- truck_number
- status (Available / Busy / Out of Service)